{"type":"message","id":"3d65f68d","parentId":"782f5a71","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:40:36.898Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Simple friendly exchange. They said thanks. I should keep it brief or just not respond - this doesn't really need a reply. A heart reaction would be natural here since the platform supports it, but Telegram reactions are in MINIMAL mode. This is a natural place to stay quiet or give a very minimal response.\n\nPer my guidelines: \"Stay silent (HEARTBEAT_OK) when: It's just casual banter... Your response would just be 'yeah' or 'nice'\"\n\nThis is one of those cases. But I already replied recently. Let me just give a minimal warm close or stay silent. I think a simple reaction or nothing is best here. Since Telegram has minimal reactions enabled, I could react. But this is very low-key... I'll just stay silent.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"NO_REPLY"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":293,"output":323,"cacheRead":20352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20968,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775104831466}}
{"type":"message","id":"7065e34c","parentId":"3d65f68d","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:41:11.142Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"643\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-02 04:41 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\"\n}\n```\n\n@Nexa_autobot  as the word manifestation came let me-ask u does manifestation really works?"}],"timestamp":1775104871139}}
{"type":"message","id":"f9b2cb3e","parentId":"7065e34c","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:41:18.064Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"They're asking about manifestation - whether it really works. This is an opinion/discussion question. I should give a thoughtful, balanced take with personality.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Honestly? It depends on what you mean by \"works.\"\n\n**Manifestation as magic** — like just thinking hard enough and the universe delivers? That's mostly wishful thinking. No credible science backs it.\n\n**But** there's something real underneath it:\n\n- **Focus & clarity** — when you \"manifest\" something, you're really just getting clear on what you want. That alone changes your decisions.\n- **Reticular activating system** — your brain literally starts noticing opportunities it would've filtered out before. Bought a new car? Suddenly you see it everywhere. Same principle.\n- **Self-fulfilling prophecy** — if you believe Friday will be chill, you walk in calmer, handle things better, and... it kinda is.\n\nSo it's not the universe responding to your vibes — it's your own brain and behavior shifting around a clear goal.\n\nWrite it down, believe it, work toward it — that combo actually does something. Just thinking about it from your couch? Not so much 😅"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":407,"output":270,"cacheRead":20608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21285,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775104871141}}
{"type":"message","id":"240b4a5b","parentId":"f9b2cb3e","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:42:36.126Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"645\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"644\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-02 04:42 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"Honestly? It depends on what you mean by \\\"works.\\\"\\n\\nManifestation as magic — like just thinking hard enough and the universe delivers? That's mostly wishful thinking. No credible science backs it.\\n\\nBut there's something real underneath it:\\n\\n• Focus & clarity — when you \\\"manifest\\\" something, you're really just getting clear on what you want. That alone changes your decisions.\\n• Reticular activating system — your brain literally starts noticing opportunities it would've filtered out before. Bought a new car? Suddenly you see it everywhere. Same principle.\\n• Self-fulfilling prophecy — if you believe Friday will be chill, you walk in calmer, handle things better, and... it kinda is.\\n\\nSo it's not the universe responding to your vibes — it's your own brain and behavior shifting around a clear goal.\\n\\nWrite it down, believe it, work toward it — that combo actually does something. Just thinking about it from your couch? Not so much 😅\"\n}\n```\n\nSo watever we want can be happened?"}],"timestamp":1775104956124}}
{"type":"message","id":"c7b9c571","parentId":"240b4a5b","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:42:42.715Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"They're asking a follow-up - can anything you want actually happen? I should give an honest, balanced answer.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Not *anything* — let's be real 😄\n\nYou can't manifest yourself into becoming 7 feet tall or winning the lottery. Some things are just physics and probability.\n\nBut the stuff within your control? Career goals, habits, relationships, skills — yeah, wanting it clearly + working toward it consistently is a genuinely powerful combo.\n\nThe trick is knowing the difference between:\n- **\"I want to be a better cook\"** → vague, nothing happens\n- **\"I'll learn one new recipe every week\"** → specific, actionable, actually works\n\nSo it's not \"everything you want will happen.\" It's more like **\"you'd be surprised how much you can shape when you stop being vague about it.\"**\n\nThe universe doesn't care about your vision board. But your own brain and daily choices? Those absolutely respond to clarity."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":718,"output":223,"cacheRead":20992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21933,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775104956126}}
{"type":"message","id":"0567b0d9","parentId":"c7b9c571","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:43:38.563Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"647\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"646\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-02 04:43 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"Not anything — let's be real 😄\\n\\nYou can't manifest yourself into becoming 7 feet tall or winning the lottery. Some things are just physics and probability.\\n\\nBut the stuff within your control? Career goals, habits, relationships, skills — yeah, wanting it clearly + working toward it consistently is a genuinely powerful combo.\\n\\nThe trick is knowing the difference between:\\n\\n• \\\"I want to be a better cook\\\" → vague, nothing happens\\n• \\\"I'll learn one new recipe every week\\\" → specific, actionable, actually works\\n\\nSo it's not \\\"everything you want will happen.\\\" It's more like \\\"you'd be surprised how much you can shape when you stop being vague about it.\\\"\\n\\nThe universe doesn't care about your vision board. But your own brain and daily choices? Those absolutely respond to clarity.\"\n}\n```\n\nOh okay"}],"timestamp":1775105018561}}
